Usage: cardano-cli latest node issue-pop-BLS --bls-signing-key-file FILEPATH
                                               --out-file FILEPATH

  Issue a BLS proof of possession

Available options:
  --bls-signing-key-file FILEPATH
                           Input filepath of the BLS signing key.
  --out-file FILEPATH      The output file.
  -h,--help                Show this help text
